{"tid":1827408,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[和你薦] 黃金經濟圈商務引薦平台","createTime":"2020-01-17T02:35:03.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-17T02:35:23.000Z","uid":161626,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"1cadfb4083312eef590aee5594c3516e29be79e4","tid":1827408,"uid":161626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-17T02:35:03.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: large;\">「黃色經濟圈」幾個月間成為港人日常生活一部份，在消費層面撐起一眾黃店，但黃色企業決定公開「出櫃」，商業打壓隨即接踵而至。近日《蘋果日報》母公司核數師以「專業風險」為由突然劈炮、網購平台「光時」遭物流界杯葛，全部都是關乎生死存亡的危機，偏偏普羅大眾欲救無從。有非建制商會正籌備B2B互助平台，冀為同路黃企穿針引線創造合作機會，擺脫受極權統戰的商家控制，長遠冀刺激更多商業聯盟出現，令本土企業達至經濟自主，成為運動強力後盾，「呢樣嘢能夠做得到，相信香港民主運動係會有一個截然不同嘅變化。」</span><br />\n<br />\n蘋果日報 <a href=\"https://bit.ly/2Rs2F6a\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2Rs2F6a&d=yrakYkBpMe8E3VCHF0kcyiLieoVo5Z%2Bt8AyiqwqBN0Y%3D&h=1379e73f\" target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/2Rs2F6a</a><br />\n<br />\n短片 <a href=\"https://fbwat.ch/1Hq060EGMd9WLrGp\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffbwat.ch%2F1Hq060EGMd9WLrGp&d=yrakYkBpMe8E3VCHF0kcyiLieoVo5Z%2Bt8AyiqwqBN0Y%3D&h=147593fe\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://fbwat.ch/1Hq060EGMd9WLrGp</a>"},{"pid":"569bc30aa3e9dbb22972bd1b06c710f364f707be","tid":1827408,"uid":325840,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-17T02:35:23.000Z","msg":"（重開）文宣 x 包裝<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1827330\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1827330</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"}]}